summary: This is an FBI evidence inventory sheet documenting the acquisition of 7 discs containing consensually monitored phone calls with Alfredo Rodriguez. The items were migrated into the evidence system on November 2, 2009.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez
persons.context: Individual whose phone calls were consensually monitored and recorded on 7 discs that were acquired as evidence by law enforcement.

events.title: Evidence acquisition of monitored calls
events.description: 7 discs containing consensually monitored phone calls with Alfredo Rodriguez were acquired and entered into evidence inventory.

keyFacts: Law enforcement conducted consensual monitoring of phone calls involving Alfredo Rodriguez.
Recordings from these monitored calls were stored on 7 discs that were entered into evidence on November 2, 2009.
The document is an FBI evidence inventory record showing the chain of custody for these recordings.
